rows.label: tlk400908_msg0001
rows.name:
Meh-meh-meh... Tora can read!
Manage to read writing!

rows.label: tlk400908_msg0008
rows.name:
But at least now we know the
general area.

rows.label: tlk400908_msg0009
rows.name:
Perhaps it's time we reported
back to Meleph.

rows.label: tlk400908_msg0010
rows.name:
Tora tell Meleph how Tora was
key to investigation success!

rows.label: tlk400908_msg0011
rows.name:
Will demand three year supply
of Tasty Sausage!

rows.label: tlk400908_msg0012
rows.name:
Don't get too carried away with
yourself there.

rows.label: tlk400908_msg0013
rows.name:
With that much Tasty Sausage,
Masterpon not need to work for
rest of life!

rows.label: tlk400908_msg0014
rows.name:
The rest of his life?
With a three-year supply?

rows.label: tlk400908_msg0016
rows.name:
If we head to the palace, the guards
should get us in touch with Meleph.

rows.label: tlk400908_msg0017
rows.name:
Yes, that was what she said.
Shall we, then?
